  during the late 1950s offutt housed a royal air force facility for servicing avro vulcans , which visited the air base frequently while on exercise with sac.   operational use of offutt air force base included the basing of alert tankers in the late 1950s and 1960s , support for intercontinental ballistic missile sites in nebraska and iowa in the 1960s , and worldwide reconnaissance from the mid-1960s to the present .

rounding the bases : on sept. 11 , 2001 this plane secretly touched down at nebraska 's offutt air force base

